biography:
DJ, Singer Songwriter & Makeup Artist 💕
Lashes & Merch: @dreamincolourbeauty

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Paying homage to some of my Queer icons marcalmondofficial @softcellhq and @boygeorgeofficial & @petshopboys with this section of my show at @thegloryldn 
With the songs ‘Say Hello Wave Goodbye’ and ‘The Cryjng Game’. Featuring the hostess with the mostess @hrhprincessjulia 
Thanks to @j.smithstudio and others for the videos ❤️❤️❤️❤️

The Disco Diva is back!!! Tonight DJ’ing at the new Trans night in London Town @temptation.tg 
Can’t wait! 
Will be spinning Disco, House, RnB, Pop, anything that Keeps the dolls dancing! 
Hosted by my girl @farrahmills2013 @iambrandyx and a whole host of other Trans beauties! 
Now, to plan my outfit!

I hadn’t heard this song for ages! 
Still proud of it! Watch the full video on my YouTube, link in bio. 
Love the beautiful video made by the talented @susaic 
I was in my mid 20’s when I wrote this with my friend Tom, and I’d already been performing and making music for years. As an unsigned independent artist and songwriter a lot of your work never gets released or sits on a hard drive never getting finished. Despite my work never getting a wider audience (yet) I’m still proud of the work I made!
What do you think? Did you know I even wrote music? This is up on YouTube, Spotify, Apple Music etc

Lucky to be part of such a beautiful community!
Here’s to many more memories this year!
@dreamincolourbeauty 
I could only tag 20 people in this but you can see all the gorgeous faces!!!
The song is one of mine ‘Transform’ it’s on Spotify etc, link in Bio girlies

Sound on LOL 😂
This was me trying to film my makeup yesterday. Cameos from my sis @isabeljtaylor and her festive boob top, and my mum trying to find her phone (this happens regularly)
Hope everyone had a nice day. 
Sending love to all those who got stuck isolating or to anyone who finds this time of year difficult xxx

Me and my friend @nicklujan_artistry sat down for @dreamincolourbeauty to have a good catch up, and to talk about Makeup, and our relationship with Drag, gender and beauty. Full video on the @dreamincolourbeauty site. Nick I love ya gurl! Thankyou for everything 💕💕💕

What a joy getting to spend time with the beautiful disco queen @lucy_fizz 
I used the new @dreamincolourbeauty palette which you can get now (but it is very limited edition so be quick!) as well as some subtle lashes LOL!
We played with makeup but also had a quick chat about her work as one of the most in demand dancers for all the best parties around the world! Make sure to check out the documentary by @glitterboxibiza which features Lucy also! 
If you come to the launch party tomorrow eve at @thegloryldn you might just get some Dream in Colour goodies HALF PRICE! And you’ll see me and the @tpartylondon girls perform our last show of 2021, plus the mega @hrhprincessjulia
Thankyou SO MUCH to my talented sis @isabeljtaylor for filming all the beautiful shots of Lucy and helping me always! So thankful for you!

Getting LASHED with @necolondon for @dreamincolourbeauty 
I used the debut eyeshadow palette which should be out this week or next (!!!) And 3 of our lash styles on the fabulous Neco. Love him so much! Which lash style is your fave on him?

Get ready with me using some of my current makeup faves! 
Including the Newly updated @kevynaucoin Sensual Skin enhancers! Such an iconic product among makeup artists. Check out @nicklujan_artistry page for more info on this amazing product.
Thanks to @tracepublicity for sending me them to try! 
I used my @dreamincolourbeauty sponges to apply and blend out, and the T-Party lashes (my fave for a subtle evening glam)
Plus the @nudestix Matte lip pencils, they are so gorgeous- long wearing and non drying 💕

latestIgtvVideos.title: Get ready with me, LIVE video lolz 👽
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I Decided to do a random live video while I was getting ready for a @dreamincolourbeauty shoot with @necolondon last week & some of my girls came on and were CRACKING me UP! Find out how much money @kuchenga owes @imoscarquiroz , why I’m never lending @antoniawoodlondon a lipstick ever again, and how my Only fans Gurls can get a Pro discount on Dream in Colour (& makeup artists and Drag queens and show girls).
Oh and there’s a sneak peak of a new @tpartylondon track!!!
